seo: 文本提取,资产获取,信息提取
seo_en: text extraction, asset acquisition, information extraction
summary: 该插件从输入文本中提取多种类型的信息，包括IP地址、域名、电话号码、电子邮件等，并根据扩展正则表达式选项进行更详细的匹配。
summary_en: This plugin extracts various types of information from the input text, including IP addresses, domains, phone numbers, emails, etc., and performs more detailed matching based on the extended regex option.
